 Endless Bummer     : X,D,X,K,D,V,K,X
 Viva Los Vagrantes : K,D,X,D,X,V,V,D

 Movie Paßwörter:

 Entrance to Uraniumania        : K,K,K,D,D,D,V,D
 Entrance to Repsychler         :   K,K,K,X,D,X,V
 Entrance to Endless Bummer     : K,K,K,V,V,D,D,X
 Entrance to Viva Los Vagrantes : K,K,K,X,X,X,V,V
 Game Over / Death              : K,K,K,K,D,K,X,K
 Game Over / Win                : K,K,K,D,X,X,D,K
 Credits                        : K,K,K,V,K,X,X,D
 Exit / Quit                    : K,K,K,D,D,K,X,V

  _________________
 |  Erklärung:  |!!|
 |--------------+--|
 |  K = KREIS   |? |
 |  X = X       | ?|
 |  V = VIERECK |? |
 |  D = DREIECK | ?|
 |______________|__|

